abstract: Rory McIlroy wins DP World Tour Championship as well as Race to Dubai title; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Rory McIlroy survived a late scare and finished his frustrating season on a high, winning both the DP World Tour Championship and the Race to Dubai crown on Sunday in Dubai, United Arab Emirates.
